info.name: SquirrelMail Address Add 1.4.2 - Cross-Site Scripting
author: dhiyaneshdk
info.description: SquirrelMail Address Add 1.4.2 plugin contains a cross-site scripting vulnerability. It fails to properly sanitize user-supplied input, thus allowing an attacker to execute arbitrary script in the browser of an unsuspecting user in the context of the affected site. This can allow the attacker to steal cookie-based authentication credentials and launch other attacks.
